Taurean Ferguson 22 Yd Fumble Return (Tommy Openshaw Kick)

videos.headline: Wildcats strike quickly
videos.description: Jojo Kemp runs up the middle for 4 yd TD as Kentucky takes 7-0 lead

videos.headline: Kentucky punt coverage forces turnover
videos.description: Vanderbilt's Ryan White fumbles punt that is recovered by Kentucky's Eli Brown

videos.headline: Kentucky extends lead with 2nd Qtr score
videos.description: Stephen Johnson fakes the handoff and runs left  for 3 yd TD as Kentucky now leads 14-3

videos.headline: Momentum shift as Vanderbilt scores on defense
videos.description: Taurean Ferguson scoops up Stanley Williams' fumble and returns it 22 yds for a TD to cut Kentucky's lead to 17-10

videos.headline: Vandy forces another turnover
videos.description: Stephen Johnson pass intercepted by Tre Herndon to give Vanderbilt good field position

videos.headline: Kentucky defense holds on 4th down to preserve 20-13 win
videos.description: Kyle Shurmur 4th down pass incomplete to Kalija Lipscomb
